text: Thank You is the second major-label studio album by American singer-songwriter Meghan Trainor. The album was released exclusively on Apple Music on May 6, 2016, and was fully released on May 13, 2016, through Epic Records. ==Track listing== ;Notes * "Woman Up" is a cover of the song of the same name by Ashley Roberts, with different lyrics. ==Release history== List of release dates, formats, label, and reference Region Date Format Label(s) Apple Music May 6, 2016 Streaming Worldwide May 13, 2016 ==References== Category:2016 albums Category:Meghan Trainor albums Category:Dance-pop albums Category:Hip hop albums Category:R&B; albums
